{
  "text": "Spelling and grammar checkers help correct student mistakes in writing (Rahmtallah 2023; McCarthy et al. 2019), while automated essay checkers (Gierl et al. 2014; Wilson & Czik 2016) and plagiarism detection tools (Foltýnek et al. 2020) facilitate the assessment of written works.",
